      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOMERTON WILLOW (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (30.71) in a Grade 5 at Sandown. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Looks the one to beat on her best form. ELUSIVE CURL (6) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage third, beaten 3.5 lengths (22.78) at Geelong in a Restricted WIN over 400m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Must be included in calculations. SWEET TRILBY (1) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 6 lengths away in second (24.56) at Sale in a Grade 5 over 435m. Ready to find winning form. ASTON KRISTEN (2) is on a run of two wins and is sure to play a big role again.",
